<p><span class="EOP SCXW21186125 BCX0" data-ccp-props="{&quot;335559685&quot;:644}"><strong>12.1</strong>&nbsp;<span class="TextRun SCXW251498999 BCX0" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="none">A qualifica&ccedil;&atilde;o t&eacute;cnica das proponentes ser&aacute; comprovada mediante apresenta&ccedil;&atilde;o dos documentos abaixo relacionados, os quais </span><span class="TextRun SCXW251498999 BCX0" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="none"><strong>DEVER&Atilde;O SER APRESENTADOS JUNTO COM OS DOCUMENTOS DE HABILITA&Ccedil;&Atilde;O</strong>, </span><span class="TextRun SCXW251498999 BCX0" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="none">no ato do certame:</span><span class="EOP SCXW251498999 BCX0" data-ccp-props="{&quot;134233279&quot;:false,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:709,&quot;335559731&quot;:0,&quot;469777462&quot;:[851],&quot;469777927&quot;:[0],&quot;469777928&quot;:[1]}">&nbsp;</span></span></p>
<p><span class="EOP SCXW21186125 BCX0" data-ccp-props="{&quot;335559685&quot;:644}"><span class="EOP SCXW251498999 BCX0" data-ccp-props="{&quot;134233279&quot;:false,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:709,&quot;335559731&quot;:0,&quot;469777462&quot;:[851],&quot;469777927&quot;:[0],&quot;469777928&quot;:[1]}"><strong>a)</strong>&nbsp;<span class="TextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">Registro ou inscri&ccedil;&atilde;o da empresa licitante e do(s) profissional (</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">is</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">): </span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><strong><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">Engenheiro Civil ou</span></strong><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0"><strong>Arquiteto e Urbanista ou T&eacute;cnico Equivalente</strong>,</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">na&nbsp;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">entidade&nbsp;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">profissional&nbsp;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">competente</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">(Conselho&nbsp;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">Regional</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">de&nbsp;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">Engenharia&nbsp;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">e&nbsp;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">Agronomia</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">- CREA ou&nbsp;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">Conselho&nbsp;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">Regional&nbsp;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">de&nbsp;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">Arquitetura e&nbsp;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">Urbanismo</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">&ndash;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">CAU). Para o licitante vencedor da licita&ccedil;&atilde;o, caso n&atilde;o seja do Acre, por ocasi&atilde;o da assinatura</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">do contrato ser&aacute; exigido o visto do Conselho de Engenharia e Agronomia - </span></span><strong><span class="TextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto">CREA </span></strong><span class="TextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">ou no&nbsp;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">Conselho&nbsp;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">de&nbsp;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">Arquitetura e&nbsp;</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">Urbanismo</span></span><span class="TextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto"><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">-</span><strong><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0">CAU</span></strong></span><span class="TextRun SCXW160778532 BCX0" lang="PT-BR" xml:lang="PT-BR" data-contrast="auto">;</span><span class="EOP SCXW160778532 BCX0" data-ccp-props="{&quot;134233279&quot;:false,&quot;335551550&quot;:6,&quot;335551620&quot;:6,&quot;335559685&quot;:2268,&quot;335559731&quot;:0,&quot;469777462&quot;:[1843],&quot;469777927&quot;:[0],&quot;469777928&quot;:[1]}">&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>
